1. For the assignment reused the code that was submitted for the Coding2-Assignment.
2. Created account in Redis Labs and MongoDB Atlas.
3. New files created as RedisDataAdapter.java and MongoDBDataAdapter.java
4. Application.java file modified to accomodate the new dataadapter file changes.
5. Existing file DataAdapter.java and it's references has been removed(Not captured in video).
6. RedisDataAdapter.java file has methods to perform load and store DB operation on users, products, credit cards, addresses classes.
7. MongoDBDataAdapter.java file has methods to perform load and store DB operation on Order details and receipts of each order classes.